    {
      "recipeDescriptionLine": "Dry fruit nut laddu is a quick and easy sweet dish that is power packed with nutrients. One can chose any kind of dry fruits to make laddos. This dish requires little jaggery for sweetness."
    },
    {
      "recipeDescriptionLine": "The dry fruits are healthy for the body and that is why these laddus are rich in protein, omega 3 fatty acids, vitamins, calcium, iron."
    }
