      "procedureSteps": [
        {
          "stepDescription": "Coarsely grind cashews, walnuts, almonds separately. Chop figs and dates in small pieces. Roast each of the powdered nuts separately in a vessel with 1 tbsp ghee and the timing is a follows: (a) Almond powder for 4 mins, (b) Cashew powder for 5 mins, (c) Walnut powder for 3 mins, (d) Dates for 3 mins,(e) Figs for 2 mins, (f) Raisins for 1 min, (g) Poppy seeds till they turn slightly brown.",
