            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "stepDescription": "Mix the roasted ingredients well and keep it aside.",
          "stepImages": [
            {
              "ImageUrl": "step_2_1.JPG",
              "ImageAltText": ""
            },
            {
              "ImageUrl": "step_2_2.JPG",
              "ImageAltText": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "stepDescription": "Crush the jaggery, melt it on a medium low flame and bring it to boil. Switch off the stove and mix crushed cardamom first, and then add the roasted ingredients. Mix it well for 5-7 mins with a spatula. Do not use hands as the jaggery is still hot.",
